---
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from "../../consts";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

interface Friend {
    name: string;
    avatar: string;
    description: string;
    link: string;
}

const friends: Friend[] = [
    {
        name: "张麦麦",
        avatar: "https://maxchang.me/favicon.svg",
        description: "我的影子想要去飞翔，我的人还在地上。",
        link: "https://maxchang.me",
    }

];
---

<Layout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
    <main>
        <h1>友情链接</h1>
        <p class="description">感谢以下朋友们的支持！欢迎交换友链 ❤️</p>

        <div class="friends-grid">
            {
                friends.map((friend) => (
                    <a
                        href={friend.link}
                        class="friend-card"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    >
                        <img
                            src={friend.avatar}
                            alt={friend.name}
                            class="avatar"
                        />
                        <div class="info">
                            <h2>{friend.name}</h2>
                            <p>{friend.description}</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                ))
            }
        </div>
        <div class="apply-section">
            <p>如果您想要申请友链，请确保您的网站满足以下条件：</p>
            <ul>
                <li>1. 网站内容健康向上</li>
                <li>2. 网站能够正常访问</li>
                <li>3. 网站为个人博客</li>
                <li>4. 网站已有一定数量的原创文章</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>如果您符合以上条件，欢迎通过以下格式<a href="https://forms.gle/WQgYQSHxfeVpr58BA" style="text-decoration:underline;">提交</a>友链申请：</p>
            <ul>
                <li>名称：您的博客名称</li>
                <li>头像：您的头像链接</li>
                <li>描述：简短的描述</li>
                <li>链接：您的博客链接</li>
            </ul>


        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1em;
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-size: 400%;
        background-position: 0%;
    }

    .description {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .friends-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); /* 两列 */
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .friend-card {
        border: 1px solid;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .friend-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .avatar {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .info h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .info p {
        margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .apply-section {
        border: 1px #63b3ed solid;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;   
    }

    .apply-section h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .apply-section ul {
        margin: 1rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .apply-section pre {
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow-x: auto;
    }
</style>
